item.description:
The Sages of RPG Gaming Group and Crackskull's Coffee & Books present a Gamenight of epic proportions.

Our first Gamenight at Crackskulls will be focusing on the best of trivia, word, and party games.  If all goes well and we get a crowd we will be hosting more with different themes!

Hope you can join us!
item.how_to_find_us: We will be the people playing games in the front area.
item.why: Gamenights are fun, and we need more of them!
